<%- include('partials/header') %>
<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>Our story, mission & vision</p>
  </div>
</div>
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <span class="section-tag">Our History</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">A Legacy of Excellence</h2>
        <p>Baliraja Career Academy was founded in 2022 by a group of passionate educators who believed every student deserves access to quality education . 
          Starting with just 40 students, we have grown into one of the most trusted coaching institutes in Maharashtra.</p>
        <p>Over the past 4+ years, we have guided Hundreads of students to achieve their dreams — from IIT aspirants to NEET toppers, and board exam achievers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-image-wrap">
        <div class="about-image-box" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e3a5f,#0f2440);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:16px;min-height:300px">
          <i class="fas fa-school" style="font-size:6rem;color:#f59e0b;opacity:0.5"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mission-vision-grid">
      <div class="mv-card">
        <div class="mv-icon"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div>
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>To provide affordable, high-quality education that empowers students from all backgrounds to achieve academic excellence and build successful careers. We believe in nurturing not just knowledge but character, discipline, and confidence.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mv-card featured">
        <div class="mv-icon"><i class="fas fa-eye"></i></div>
        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
        <p>To be Maharashtra's most trusted coaching academy, known for producing well-rounded, academically excellent, and socially responsible students who make a positive difference in the world.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mv-card">
        <div class="mv-icon"><i class="fas fa-heart"></i></div>
        <h3>Our Values</h3>
        <p>Integrity, dedication, and student-first approach form the core of everything we do. We foster a supportive learning environment where every student is encouraged to reach their fullest potential.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
